{
  "stem": "10353.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "She couldn't get through the Elbe River, because they were cut off, 'til finally they found one place where we-- they-- they got through.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And after several days of travel, we finally came into Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "In Theresienstadt, we were thrown into a pit that apparently was an old castle.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And this was the back part of a castle with a tunnel underneath.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "And it was a very, very rainy day, I remember.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "And we were kept there for a couple of days.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "During the night, we sort of managed to smuggle into that tunnel, to try to be shielded from-- from the rain.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "And we were-- about two days later, we were marched out from there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "And we were taken into one of the armories, because Theresienstadt was composed of many armories.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were taken into the-- what was it called now, the name of the city?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Dresdner Kaserne, I think it was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were billeted in there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And now this was already solid buildings-- it wasn't barracks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Solid buildings.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was-- for our group, I was given the task to haul coal from the basement up to the second floor where the kitchen was situated.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there it was regularly given already soup every-- every day.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had to haul that coal back and forth.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then, at night, we were given the task to clean up the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had a little bit of privilege.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We got a little bit of extra soup for that work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But we knew that typhoid was on the breakout.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We heard already isolated cases.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Every day you heard more and more that typhoid is breaking out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And this was going on 'til [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] May, May 9th.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
